  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aim to be the fastest conqueror in the world with special moves and the strongest build!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After receiving the response from the beta test and NextFest, it was reborn as Speedrun!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Maximum 10 minutes. Aim for the fastest time with time attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key is how quickly you can enter Isekai Musou mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Hell class monster wave!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By using the \"Enemy Summoning Flute\", you can create a [Hell-Class Monster Wave] that even surpasses the Survivor-like monster wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Special Skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Skills are special skills that can be used by filling up a gauge, allowing you to aim at enemies like a shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Boss standing in your wayBy defeating the demon generals enshrined in a specific area, you can acquire powerful skills that can only be obtained there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aim to be the fastest conqueror in the world with special moves and the strongest build!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After receiving the response from the beta test and NextFest, it was reborn as Speedrun!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Maximum 10 minutes. Aim for the fastest time with time attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key is how quickly you can enter Isekai Musou mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Hell class monster wave!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By using the \"Enemy Summoning Flute\", you can create a [Hell-Class Monster Wave] that even surpasses the Survivor-like monster wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/72c5ea547e1936c7651a47e482dc1692.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Special Skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Skills are special skills that can be used by filling up a gauge, allowing you to aim at enemies like a shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/ba66396333e34ff235f3393a50a8ea61.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Boss standing in your wayBy defeating the demon generals enshrined in a specific area, you can acquire powerful skills that can only be obtained there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.poster.avif?t=1741137569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.webm?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804020/extras/abd4cf323437617f244e21988cf9130e.mp4?t=1741137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
